item.title: Husky AI walkthrough and threat model
item.description:
In the previous post I talked about learning resources for AI/ML. Now it’s time to dive into details on building a model and application we can perform security testing on. In this post I’ll describe how I built Husky AI, an application that can identify if an image contains a husky or not.
If you watched the show Silicon Valley, you might find this quite funny. In particular we will cover the following topics:
